      </div>
      <div class="col-md-3 text-center p-3 box ">
        <h1> <i class="bi bi-people-fill"></i></h1>
        <h2>Research</h2>
        <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Molestias, eligendi?Lorem ipsum dolor, sit amet
          consectetur adipisicing elit. Aliquam, vel?</p>
